{"tid":840960,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人大左 好多野都變曬咁","createTime":"2018-09-29T08:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T12:56:25.000Z","uid":146103,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"36f9250236ab929c7a4a2b87f9bd5793abc8990f","tid":840960,"uid":146103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:08:51.000Z","msg":"細個, 好渴望可以大個,<br />\n因為大人既世界入面可以做到好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到真係大左, 讀緊中學 可能又為公開試去拼命<br />\n當考到唔差既成績<br />\n入到唔差既出黎 做野又好似唔係個回事咁<br />\n每日真係為個五斗米而折腰 行屍走肉咁番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打開部電話, 想搵以前稱兄道弟既好友, <br />\n發覺對上一次chat 已經係好耐咁<br />\n可能每年見得一兩次<br />\n但一見總會唔知邊度傾起<br />\n大家讀既科 從事行業已經唔同曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n在學時, 每日放學 番屋企食晚飯,<br />\n總會嫌老母 :「又係呢d餸呀, 煮第d啦」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n升上u, 晚晚出去 發現其實老母煮既野真係好好味<br />\n到出黎做野 搬埋出黎<br />\n一星期可能得一晚會番屋企食老母既餸,<br />\n然而老母就會煮最好食既野俾自己食<br />\n有時老豆老母會去旅行 一個月可能得個一日番去食<br />\n個餐老母就會話「出去食啦 邊度既打邊爐放題抵食呀」<br />\n係呢個moment會好掛住老母親手煮既飯菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n朋友, 家人好似已經離自己越黎越遠咁<br />\n唔開心又可以點? 訓醒一教 第日又要番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以前中學, 操中文past-paper 有份卷叫「只能陪你一程」<br />\n其實篇文講得好岩,  所有人,事,物只係可以陪自己一程<br />\n到適當既時候, 就會有下個人出現, 或者個個時候已經唔洗人陪了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唉屌  我淨係想好似以前咁做個on9仔日日番學放學咋 唔想做野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a065e478d7f2aec73602f3791a6e19300ba827","tid":840960,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:12:09.000Z","msg":"一句講曬下午茶食乜好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef964cfe93db63385be4369d30c0d09cedb5154","tid":840960,"uid":71496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女都無"},{"pid":"ba847fed693ef1b7c42f1458f21f2166035993a6","tid":840960,"uid":74927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:14:59.000Z","msg":"樓主你post 親都咁重負能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好再開post 啦好嗎"},{"pid":"127fd81bad3f8b75f9a0ac44acc2b807707e7a57","tid":840960,"uid":68081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:17:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 只能用一句結尾: 往事只能回味<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"d38154a7696ecd4ec222a96889c25820919513ad","tid":840960,"uid":175208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T08:32:33.000Z","msg":"Sad"},{"pid":"b47182bf50f034d74a61b12ce5a477b40dec826f","tid":840960,"uid":191555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T09:49:03.000Z","msg":"我到而家都係覺得老母煮既野都係咁難食<br />\n而事實都係"},{"pid":"f4f81cb163c57e123643b6743f7381a457d1ac9c","tid":840960,"uid":65177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T12:56:25.000Z","msg":"算吧喇"}]}